(1, 'Web producer', 1, 3, 17, 'The WEB producer is the job of grasping the entire flow from the upstream to the downstream process in the Web business and supervising it as the person in charge.\n \nWe will build the necessary system by planning and strategy planning of WEB services and contents such as Web media, EC sites, online game, smartphone applications.\n \nIn the manufacturing process, we will publish the service while managing quality and risk, and even after the release, we will continue to consider and direct the implementation of measures necessary for growth.\n \nAt first glance, it may seem glamorous, but most of them are devoted to the care of project members and related companies, and sometimes they are hated, but they also play the role of commander who motivates members and brings out performance toward the success of the project. increase.', 'Design service concepts and user experiences (UX) based on trends obtained from daily information gathering and analysis of marketing data, and grow services through PDCA.\nCoordinate the activities of directors, designers, engineers, and other personnel after launching a project, planning and budgeting, and obtaining approval from the authorizer.\nStudy planning ideas using drinking parties, the Internet, seminars, exhibitions, communities, and any other source of information.\nReview test services and prototypes and provide feedback in terms of quality, usability, accessibility, etc. required by the service.\nCheck the risks hidden in services such as security and compliance, and consider countermeasures in advance.', 'Document editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nWEB editing (Adobe, Wordpress, etc.)\nSNS editing (Facebook, Instagram, twitter, etc.)\nProject management (Backlog, Github, Redmine, etc.)\nMarketing (Google Analytics, MA tools, Userlocal, etc.)\nAdvertising operation (Google Ads, SSP, DSP)\nCloud management (aws, azure, gcp, dropbox, etc.)', 'Business / service development\nBusiness plan, sales management', 'WEB production company\nMedia, games, e-commerce companies\nIT startup company\nOwned media of major companies\nBusiness development of mid-sized companies', 'Information gathering\nPlanning\nProgress confirmation\nData confirmation\nResource adjustment\nreview\nfeedback\nfollow up', 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Designer (male)', '22.00', '420.00', 'Starting salary: 220,000 WEB designers as a whole (male) 20-24\nAverage: 350,000 WEB designers 1000 people or more (male) average', 'None', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 6, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 15:53:27', NULL),
(2, 'Data Scientist Data Analyst', 1, 3, 13, 'A data scientist / data analyst is a job that handles incomplete and huge amounts of data, and makes full use of statistical analysis and IT skills to structure and organize it.\n \nHow can the organized data be used in the business and how can the business or company generate profits? It is also included in my work to systematically think about this, formulate a predictive model, and put it into actual operation.\n\nSince we handle a wide variety of data depending on the type of business and business type, knowledge of a wide range of IT businesses is required. In recent years, AI has made it more efficient, and human intuition is also required.', 'We handle huge amounts of data, make full use of statistical analysis and IT skills to structure and organize, find the data necessary for business strategy, and change it into data that can be utilized through analysis and verification.\nFrom requirements definition to find problems, data collection to collect data necessary for problem solving, data conversion to make it easier to see using graphs, data analysis to verify the cause and verification of problems, and analysis results It is collation with analysis results and sharing of results to verify the solution of the problem and present the information.\nSince this is a job that requires a wide range of skills, I will participate in study sessions and seminars to hone the skills required in each of the fields of business, data analysis, and IT.', 'Introduction and setting of data analysis tools\nHypothesis and goal setting\nAnalysis using data analysis tools\nReport creation and improvement plan', 'Data infrastructure\nData manging\nStatistics\nMultivariable calculus\nLinear algebra\nMachine learning\nData visualization\nProgramming\nSoftware design\nMarketing', 'Web-based companies that develop services such as EC sites and social games\nManufacturing industry\nAdvertising agency\nAudit corporation\nConsulting company\nSIer', 'Project design\nData collection,\nDatabase construction\nData processing\nData analysis\nData visualization and processing\nevaluation\nBusiness planning\npresentation\nMaintenance and operation', 1, 1, 1, 1, 'System engineer (male)', '25.40', '492.00', 'Starting salary: 254,000 yen (company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 410,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age total)', 'None', '3,400 people', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 5, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 15:53:35', NULL),
(3, 'Insurance Directors', 3, 7, 25, 'An insurance salesperson is a job that visits ordinary households and businesses and provides consulting and sales of insurance products according to the lifestyle and needs of each customer.\n \nWe recommend that you take out insurance by providing information on appropriate insurance products while resolving your anxieties and doubts based on your knowledge of insurance and taxes.\n \nAfter-sales service after taking out insurance is also important, and we will review the contract details according to changes in lifestyle and introduce special contracts and new products as necessary to build a long-term relationship of trust with customers.\n\nContracts are largely dependent on personal connections, such as referrals from acquaintances and customers, and activities to build a wide range of human relationships are required on a daily basis.', 'We visit general households and businesses and provide consulting and sales of insurance products according to the lifestyle and needs of each customer.\nWe explain insurance products using leaflets and pamphlets, and provide information on appropriate insurance products and recommend insurance while resolving customer concerns and doubts based on the knowledge of insurance and taxes that we have acquired. increase.\nIn order to emphasize personal connections, we also participate in events and distribute e-mail newsletters in order to make a wide range of friendships.\nAs an after-sales service after taking out insurance, we will confirm payment, review the contract contents according to the customer\'s age and changing lifestyle, and introduce special contracts and new products as necessary, etc. I will build it.', 'Document editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nSimulator operation (PC, tablet)\nDialogue communication\nProduct description, proposal, negotiation', 'Financial product knowledge\nLife plan\nTax system, pension, social insurance\nInheritance, gift\nBusiness succession\nReal estate\nRis