(28, 'Journalist', 4, 5, 26, 'Newspaper reporters are responsible for collecting information on various fields related to our lives, such as politics, economy, society, culture, regions, and sports, and creating and editing newspaper articles.\n\nIn order to create a good newspaper article, it is important to have accurate information and writing ability to convey it to the reader in an easy-to-understand manner, but it is also important to have the ability to collect information with a high antenna and build a wide network of contacts.\n\nNewspaper reporters are on the decline as a whole due to the efficiency of coverage via the Internet and SNS, but the writing ability cultivated in newspapers that require accuracy is useful, and it is also active in WEB media and specialized magazines. You can expect a place.', 'Newspaper articles are often in charge of different fields such as politics, economy, society, culture, region, and sports, but local newspapers and industry newspapers may be in charge of all fields.\nNewspaper reporters include reporters who conduct investigations and interviews on the details of primary information, reporters who collect interviews and put them together in a manuscript, and typographical errors, omissions, copyrights, and reliability of information in order to create accurate sentences. There are reviewers who confirm the information, and photo reporters who mainly take pictures, and each of them shares and cooperates to complete the article.\nIn order to obtain the information that is the basis of the article as soon as possible, we will conduct investigations by companies, organizations, governments, police, etc., and make adjustments so that the information will be sent as soon as possible. In addition, we conduct daily Investigations and interviews to obtain unique information.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nManuscript writing\nSentence expression\nSentence structure, edit\nProofreading, review', 'Common sense\n