(30, 'Affiliate', 1, 3, 46, 'Affiliators are jobs that earn performance-based income from advertisements posted on their websites and blogs.\n\nWe will narrow down the products that will be advertised and create websites and blogs accordingly. Select an affiliate advertisement that handles the product to be posted, and create an article to be advertised after screening.\nWe will analyze the site so that it will be more effective, and we will improve and update the SEO measures and the site.\n\nMost of the income of affiliates is performance-based compensation type such as the number of clicks on advertisements and the number of products and purchases via advertisements, and since it can be easily introduced on blogs etc. There are various people who earn millions of yen.', 'Set up websites and blogs about your area of ​​expertise and themes you are interested in, and write articles for which you want to place affiliate ads.\nTo place an affiliate advertisement, register with an affiliate company, select the advertisement you want to place from multiple advertisers, and apply. Since there is an advertiser\'s review before posting, we will apply to multiple advertisers at the same time and pass the review.\nAfter passing the screening, we will embed an advertisement-specific tag in the appropriate part of the article and place the advertisement. If necessary, we will post impressions of trying out products and services, take pictures, and take other measures to attract readers\' interest.\nAfter posting, we will analyze the number of visits to the site and the behavior of readers, and consider SEO measures and configurations that will be more interesting in the article so that the number of visitors will increase.\nIf you succeed as an affiliate, we will also carry out activities to further expand your business domain through seminars and consulting that make use of your successful experience, knowledge, and know-how.', 'Site production\nAccess analysis\nWriting\nSentence expression\nAdvertising selection and operation\nOperation of SNS', 'How to use the delivery platform\nSEO\nWeb analytics\nMarketing\nKeyword selection\nProgramming', 'One\'s home\nPersonal Office work place\nCorporate', 'Marketing\nAdvertising selection\nLighting\nCreate, modify and manage blogs and websites', 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '0.00', '0.00', '1,000 yen to several million yen / month', 'None', '3,870,000 people', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 15:58:45', NULL),
(31, 'Professional gamer', 2, 4, 47, 'Professional gamers do a variety of game-related work, such as participating in game competitions, earning prize money, and engaging in game development as a player.\n\nResearch the content and strategy of the game in your specialty field and improve your skill in game operation. We may also sign a sponsorship contract with a game company to perform event demonstrations and instructors. Popular professional gamers also hold fan events. I may also be involved in publishing strategy guides and testing and developing games.\n\nRecently, gameplay as an e-sport and a competitive sport has spread worldwide, and the prize money at the competition has reached hundreds of millions of yen. In addition, some people earn money by playing live games on video distribution sites and appearing on online game programs.', 'Select a game to play from your favorite game or your favorite game, study its contents and strategy, and practice the operation of the game. As an activity, I hope to be a freelancer or a team member to hone my playing skills and participate in the tournament.\nIn recent years, games as competitive sports have become more active as e-sports, and competition with players from powerful countries such as the United States, China, and South Korea has also intensified.\nIn e-sports, prizes amounting to hundreds of millions of yen are not uncommon, and there are times when we travel abroad to participate in competitions or move our activity bases overseas.\nProfessional players often make sponsorship contracts with game companies and companies that provide related products, and also carry out promotions and negotiations to acquire sponsors. When a sponsor is acquired, it will be promoted as an advertising tower, and will be demonstrated at events, lecturers, and product advice.\nAs a professional player, individual activities are also important, and we hold exchange events with fans such as autograph sessions and handshake events, and respond to fans by distributing videos on SNS and Youtube.\nIf you become a first-class player, you may be involved in game development, and we will also give planning advice and play tests, and will disseminate information on the content and strategies of the game as public relations on blogs and websites.', 'Game operation\nVideo creation and distribution\nOperation of SNS', 'Knowledge of the game in general\nStrategy\nVideo creation and distribution', 'Freelance\nGame company', 'Training\nTournament participation\nLecture\nMedia appearance\nFan support\nVideo creation and distribution\nWriting', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Not Applicable', '0.00', '0.00', 'Tens of thousands to hundreds of millions of yen', 'None', 'Dozens of people. About 55 million people worldwide', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 15:58:51', NULL),
(32, 'YouTuber', 3, 7, 27, 'Youtuber is a job to post original videos on youtube and create videos of requested product introductions to earn advertising revenue.\n\nBy raising the antenna on a daily basis and collecting information such as changes and trends in the world, we collect video planning ideas. After shooting and editing the video, set an ad and post it on youtube.\nIn the case of youtuber, which has a certain degree of popularity, some people make contracts with companies such as manufacturers to produce commercial videos and product introduction videos.\n\nSince differentiation and individuality from other youtubers are important, there are various youtubers such as those who master special skills such as music and sports, and those who show individuality with visual appearance, and it is attracting attention as a profession that youth longs for. ..', 'We usually raise the antenna high, collect information such as changes and trends in the world, plan videos that are likely to be talked about, shoot and edit.\nWhen creating a video, we perform location hunting (location hunting) such as a place that attracts more interest or a place that is visually good for the video, decide the shooting location, and shoot.\nWe will edit the recorded video, such as adding audio, sound effects, and animation to the video, to create a work that can be viewed more.\nWe will post a video of the created work on youtube, set an advertisement and when distribution starts, we will promote the video on SNS and blogs with the aim of entering the trend and carry out activities to earn more views.\nAs popularity and popularity increase, activities to support promotion such as planning and producing tie-up videos with products and services will also occur at the request of companies.', 'Marketing\nAdvertising selection and operation\nVideo planning\nMovie shooting\nDirecting\nVideo editing\nCopywriting\nTalk\nOperation of SNS', 'Wide range of trend knowledge\nDigital knowledge\nEx