(33, 'Instagrammer', 3, 7, 27, 'Instagrammer is a job to earn income by posting photos on Instagram, a photo sharing SNS, and introducing products at the request of companies.\n\nThe major points are the technology for taking Instagram-worthy photos that make the best use of your own special skills and visuals, and the image processing technology that utilizes editing apps.\nIn particular, a user who has a large number of followers and views and has a strong influence is called an influencer, and by utilizing his knowledge and know-how related to his specialty, he provides columns to specialized magazines and web media, and has knowledge about Instagram. We also hold seminars and consulting that make use of our know-how.\nNot only celebrities and celebrities, but also many general users specializing in some genre, the top Instagrammers in each genre have millions of followers and are the opinion leaders on that road.', 'You need a lot of followers to become an Instagrammer, so I will take advantage of my specialty and visuals to take pictures that look good on Instagram and post them to acquire followers.\nIn order to post photos that look good on Instagram, I always keep an antenna on the products and locations of the topic, go to shoot quickly, and study the composition that looks better every day.\nIt is also important for Instagram to process the photos taken with a dedicated editing app, etc., and we will also collect information on the latest editing apps and learn how to operate them.\nIn order to respond to requests from companies to introduce products, based on requests from companies, we will actually verify the effects of using products, capture the process in photos, prepare images that will look good on Instagram, and post. I will do it.\nTop Instagrammers utilize their knowledge and know-how in their fields of expertise to provide columns to specialized magazines and web media, to become product advisors, and to jointly develop original products.\nIn addition, we will respond to requests for seminars and consulting that utilize our knowledge and know-how regarding Instagram.', 'Photo shoot\nImage editing\nCopywriting\nOperation of Biog\nOperation of SNS', 'Wide range of trend knowledge\nDigital knowledge\nExpression method', 'One\'s home\nPersonal Office work place', 'Collecting material\nPlanning\nInformation and material collection\nphotograph\nedit\nupload\nUser follow\nSponsor support', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reporter (male)', '32.50', '750.00', 'Starting salary: 325,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 625,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'None', 'Not clear', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 6, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 15:59:03', NULL),
(34, 'Professional blogger', 3, 7, 27, 'A professional blogger is the job of writing professional articles on his blog to earn advertising and billing income.\n\nSimilar to affiliates, but affiliates aim to write articles for the products they advertise, while bloggers aim to make money from the articles they write. You can make money by publishing articles in your specialty and paying for the advertisements and articles that appear in the articles.\n\nIn addition, we may provide columns to information sites and web media by utilizing our knowledge and know-how related to our specialty fields, and hold seminars and consulting utilizing our knowledge and know-how related to blogs.', 'We will set up an information blog about your hobbies and your specialty.\nRegister with a business that handles content-linked advertising such as Google Adsense, and after passing the screening, we will arrange to embed an advertisement-specific tag and place the advertisement on your blog or website.\nAfter posting, we will analyze the number of visits to the site and the behavior of readers, and create SEO measures and articles that are more interesting to increase the number of visitors.\nBy publishing high-quality articles and increasing the number of viewers, we will respond to article contribution requests from other information sites and Web media.\nIf you become a popular blogger, we will hold seminars and consulting that make use of your knowledge and know-how about blogging.', 'Marketing\nBlog site construction\nSite management\nAccess analysis\nLighting\nTaking photos and videos\nEditing images and videos\nOperation of SNS', 'Common sense\nDeep knowledge of the field to convey in the blog\nSEO', 'One\'s home\nPersonal Office work place', 'Planning study\nCollecting material\nCoverage\nphoto shoot\nConstitution\nwriting\nProofreading\nUp to the site', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reporter (male)', '32.50', '750.00', 'Starting salary: 325,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage