(35, 'Game caster', 3, 7, 27, 'Game casters are jobs that excite the audience and viewers while explaining the situation of the game in an easy-to-understand manner at competitive game competitions such as e-sports.\n\nWithout a game caster who can explain and explain the game situation in an easy-to-understand manner as in the case of sports, only those who can understand the development of the game, such as the player\'s super play and psychological play, will know. In addition, in order to know the personal part of each player who participates in the tournament, we will conduct preliminary interviews and research to broaden the depth and breadth of commentary.\n\nDisseminate your own activities and information through the game community, SNS, youtube, etc., and spread the enjoyment of the game. With the expansion of e-sports, there are increasing opportunities for announcers to become game casters, but it is required to develop casters who have a solid knowledge of games.', 'Research the game that gives your own commentary and commentary, and research the features and capture points in advance. In addition, we will conduct investigations of participating players and conduct hearings in advance to understand the characteristics and habits of play.\nEnliven the audience and viewers while providing easy-to-understand live commentary on the competition situation at game competitions such as e-sports.\nAs an activity to receive requests from the tournament, we will disseminate our own activities and information in the game community, SNS, game events, etc. in order to acquire fans.\nBy gaining a bird\'s-eye view of a lot of information about the game and building relationships with players, we will also acquire corporate sponsors who provide related products, perform at events, and write strategies.', 'Game operation\nVocalization, smooth tongue\nLive commentary\nSpeaking ability, how to take a break\nFacilitation', 'Game knowledge\nVocabulary\nPsychology', 'Event pla