(40, 'Web designer', 2, 4, 18, 'Web designers are the jobs of designing, producing and coding websites, e-commerce sites, game apps, etc.\n\nWhile checking the site map and wire frame created by the web director, create a design that is easy for the website user to use and a web design that matches the image of the client, and cooperate with system engineers and programmers on the web. Complete the site.\n\nRecently, websites have been easily launched by CMS and cloud services, and the weight of total design such as usability and accessibility according to the purpose of use is increasing as well as design elements.', 'While checking the site map and wireframe, we will consider the web design that suits the purpose of use of the website and the image of the client, and create design samples and prototypes.\nIn order to create the design of the website and process the photos and images to be used, we will create the design by making full use of graphic software such as Illustrator and Photoshop.\nIn order to make the website easy to use for the purpose of use of the requester and the user who uses the site, we will research other websites and conduct research on people who are close to the user target to create a design.\nIn order to complete the website, we will build the website in cooperation with system engineers and programmers, and complete the site after checking and modifying with the web director and web producer.', 'Web design planning and planning\nDesign (Illustrator, Photoshop)\nProgram coding\nProgramming\nOperation of web production software', 'HTML\nCSS\nPHP\nJavaScript\nSEO\nIntellectual property right\nCopyright', 'Web production company\nWeb charge for general companies\nFreelance', 'Whole page image\nHTML and CSS coding\nProduction of image part\nCreating dynamic objects\nTimely correction', 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Designer (male)', '22.50', '546.00', 'Starting salary: 225,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 455,000 yen (1,000 people or m