(41, 'Fashion designer', 2, 4, 18, 'A fashion designer is the job of designing clothes, shoes, bags and other apparel and sending them out to the world.\n\nWe will decide the direction of the design that we are aiming for, research what kind of fashion will be popular according to the image of the brand, and create the design.\n\nFashion designers include haute couture designers who create their own brands and create original designs, and in-house designers who belong to brands and manufacturers. There are free designers who decide the affiliation.\n\nRecently, it has become possible to publish your own designs on websites and SNS, and you need not only artistic sense, but also promotion power to sell yourself and marketing power to make clothes that sell well.', 'Investigate the design you want to do, your favorite fashion, trends, etc. and consider the direction of the design.\nOnce the direction is decided, the concept is put together in a plan, a design picture is created, the sewing method and materials are selected, a sample is created, and when the sample is finished, corrections are made and details are squeezed.\nFor commercialization, we will clarify the target, sales channel, production quantity, etc., manage costs and delivery dates, give instructions to pattern designers, and supervise until completion.\nAfter completion, we will shoot the catalog, check the display, sales method, etc. We are also involved in planning and supervising exhibitions and fashion shows.', 'Marketing Research\nSketches and drawings\nDraping\nPattern making', 'Knowledge of sewing\nKnowledge of fabric\nDesign knowledge\nHuman skeleton\nHistory of trends\nMarketing\nSales promotion', 'Apparel maker\nTextile manufacturer\nDesign Office work place\nPrivate boutique\nClothing brand\nFreelance\nIndependent opening', 'Market research\nPlanning meeting\nCreating design drawings and fashion drawings\nProduct planning\nFabric selection\nPattern creation\nCutting\nSewing', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'De