(42, 'Movie producer', 2, 4, 18, 'Film producers are responsible for everything from planning new films to financing, production and copyright management, and sales collection.\n\nAt the planning meeting, we will consider planning a new movie that is likely to be popular in the future. Since a huge amount of money is required for movie production, we will build personal connections such as companies on a daily basis and raise the funds necessary for movie production. At the same time, we will select the staff necessary for film production and formulate a production schedule.\nOnce the production begins, we will take command of the scene with the director and director to complete the film.\nDecide on a movie theater to promote the completed movie, think about a promotion plan, and collect sales.\n\nWhereas film directors are responsible for the quality of their work, film producers are in an important position to take responsibility for the entertainment of the film. Recently, the division of labor with the director has progressed, and the number of people actively involved in promotions is increasing.', 'Since many people and funds are needed to make a movie, we will build personal connections such as companies on a daily basis and raise the funds necessary for making a movie.\nFrom the planning meetings and talks with the director, we will consider interesting ideas and plans for new movies that are likely to be popular in the future, create planning concepts and plots (synopsis), and raise funds from sponsors.\nWhen the production of the movie is decided, the main staff such as the movie director and the scriptwriter are decided, the production committee including the sponsor is organized, and the production schedule is set. After that, we will organize the cast and production staff.\nIn production, I work with the director and director to raise the command of the production site and participate in editing.\nWhen the movie is completed, we will decide which movie 