(43, 'Music producer', 2, 4, 18, 'A music producer is the chief conductor of all aspects of music product production, from sound source production tailored to sales and intended use to music used in live concerts and movies.\n\nCoordinating with artists and production companies according to the usage such as album sales and movie music, from creative work such as selection and creation of songs to be provided, selection and coordination of music creators such as lyrics and composers, securing of budget We even do practical work such as management.\n\nIn addition to music production, we also cooperate with sales and entertainment, designing CD jackets, shooting and producing promotional videos and photographs, responding to mass media, and stage production in consideration of concert planning.\n\nThere are many fans who aim for the sound produced by the producer, and the role of the producer is increasing in sales and entertainment.', 'We will discuss music planning and concepts in consultation with artists and production companies according to the album sales and the works to be produced.\nIn the production of music, music creators such as lyricists, composers, and arrangers are selected according to the plan to create the music. In many cases, he writes and composes himself.\nIn order to record the produced music, we select studios, engineers, and studio musicians, take the lead in the actual sound production, arrange them, and complete the work.\nIn addition to music, we also design jackets that make up the product, and shoot and produce promotional videos and photographs.\nIn order to successfully sell and entertain the products, we also support the mass media, appear on TV and magazines, respond to interviews, and plan concerts to create the stage.', 'Music business planning and planning\nProject Management\nMusical instrument performance\nDirecting\nrecording\nMixer operation', 'General knowledge of music\nDigital knowledge\nBusiness Planning\nBudget, accountin