(56, 'Business consultant', 6, 5, 20, 'A management consultant is a job that supports the formulation of management strategies and personnel strategies of companies, and M & A (merger and acquisition of companies).\n\nThere are a wide range of request fields such as management improvement, business planning, and acquisition of companies, but we investigate the cause and propose solutions by grasping the management status and investigating and analyzing the problems.\n\nIn addition, I also hold management seminars for companies and instruct employee skill development seminars.\n\nThere are various things such as belonging to a consulting firm or doing it individually, but there are no qualifications to become a management consultant, and in many cases you have a degree such as MBA (Master of Business Administration).', 'The fields requested are not only management knowledge but also business because there are various fields such as management strategy, finance / accounting, new business planning, M & A (merger and acquisition of companies), production efficiency, organization / personnel strategy, sales / marketing strategy, etc. We collect information and learn about services and services.\nWe analyze the request and situation of the client, carry out Investigation, formulate a strategy, and create an implementation plan.\nBased on the management strategy and implementation plan requested, we may participate in the organization or business and take command and execute it hands-on.\nHe also holds management seminars for business owners and entrepreneurs, and also teaches employee skill development seminars.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\ncommunication\nMarketing Research\nManagement diagnosis\nFinding and solving problems\nPresentation\nProject Management', 'Economic trends\nKnowledge of law\nAnalytical method\nGeneral management knowledge', 'Consulting company\nFreelance\nIndependent opening', 'Hearing\nDiagnose\nInvestigation\nAnalysis\nIssue id