(57, 'Certified public accountant', 4, 5, 20, 'A certified accountant is a job that checks the management status based on the financial statements of companies, school corporations, public interest corporations, etc., and performs audit work that makes recommendations as an expert.\n\nAs an expert, we check the financial statements from the perspective of a third party and ensure the credibility of the company.\nAudit work includes statutory audits required by laws and regulations and audits other than statutory audits. As a consultant, there are also people who provide consultation and advice on overall management, and work in the corporate planning office and finance department of general companies.\n\nCertified accountants are the highest national examination in accounting, and are said to be the three major professionals along with doctors and lawyers. Auditing, which is the main business, is an exclusive business that only accountants are allowed to do. The passing rate of the certified accountant examination is about 10%, which is a narrow gate.', 'As a statutory audit business, we check the financial statements of companies listed on the stock exchange and large companies with capital of 500 million yen or more, and confirm that the company is operating correctly and false figures. Make sure that there is no Financial Statement to be stated.\nAs a consultant with expertise in accounting and finance, we provide consultation and advice on all aspects of management, including management strategy planning, organizational restructuring, and system consulting.\nThere are also people who work in the corporate planning office of general companies, such as IR that deals with shareholders and investors, due diligence that evaluates corporate value in M & A, etc., and as a person in charge of accounting and finance in the finance department. increase.\nBy registering as a tax accountant, you can perform tax duties such as preparing and filing tax documents in the same way as a tax accountant.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nAccounting software, system operation\nFinding and solving financial and accounting issues\nPresentation\nFinancial planning\nAccounting audit', 'Accounting\nAudit theory\nCorporate law\nBusiness Administration\nEconomics\nCivil Code\nStatistics', 'Audit corporation\nAccounting department of a general company\nCertified Accountant Office work office', 'Customer visit\nChecking business conditions\nCheck accounting and settlement of accounts\nConsulting\nAudit document preparation', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Certified accountant, tax accountant (male)', '36.30', '910.80', 'Starting salary: 363,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 759,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'None', '16,222人', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 16:03:21', NULL),
(58, 'Social Insurance Laborer', 7, 8, 23, 'A social insurance labor consultant is a job that acts on behalf of employees who belong to a company based on the law on social insurance and labor. A professional who is familiar with social insurance and labor law.\n\nOn behalf of the company, we perform procedures and documents related to employee social insurance and labor insurance, as well as payroll calculation and work rules.\nWe also provide consulting and in-house training at the request of corporations and individuals. , Procedures for pensions and industrial accidents, as well as consultation and advice.\n\nIn recent years, there has been increasing interest in diverse work styles and working environments, and there is an increasing demand for social insurance labor consultants who can utilize their specialized knowledge to provide personnel, recruitment consulting, and corporate training, as well as procedures and document preparation.', 'Laws related to the employment of employees of companies (Labor Standards Law, Labor Accident Insurance Law, Employment Insurance Law, Health Insurance Law, Labor Contract Law, Equal Employment Opportunity Law, Childcare / Nursing Care Leave Law, etc. ) Confirmation of changes and information gathering\nAt the request of companies, we will act on behalf of health insurance, employment insurance, workers\' accident compensation insurance, payroll, etc., and create worker lists, wage ledgers, work rules, etc.\nWe provide consulting services related to personnel and labor, such as staffing in corporate organizations, subsidy applications, and in-house education.\nAt the request of the worker, we will carry out procedures such as pension arbitrage claim procedures and workers\' accident compensation insurance benefit application procedures.\nWe also provide pension advice for corporations and individuals.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nHuman Resource Management\nPension management\nPresentation', 'Labor Standards Act\nIndustrial Accident Insurance Law\nEmployment Insurance Law\nHealth Insurance Act\nLabor contract law\nEqual Employment Act\nChildcare / Nursing Care Leave Law', 'Social Insurance Labor and Social Security Attorney Office work office\nGeneral company (personnel / labor)\nAgency\nIndependent opening', 'Customer visit\nHearing\nAssignment settings\nInvestigation of solutions\nCreation of proposal materials\nSuggestions, explanations\nRule making, procedure agency\nDelivery, reporting', 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Social insurance labor consultant (female)', '16.00', '298.80', 'Starting salary: 160,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 249,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'It is necessary to satisfy one of the eligibility for the examinations of educational background, practical experience, and passing other national examinations.', '40,426人', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 6, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 16:03:31', NULL),
(59, 'Career consultant', 7, 8, 23, 'A career consultant is a job that provides advice and guidance in response to consultations regarding worker choices, occupational life planning, or development and improvement of vocational abilities.\n\nThrough interviews with counselors, you will be aware of your aptitude, abilities, interests, etc., deepen your self-understanding, and by understanding the work in society and the company, you can proactively select the work that suits you. I will support you so that you can. If you think you need treatment, such as a mental illness, we encourage you to refer a specialist or get into a state of mind to see a psychiatrist.\n\nCareer consultants become national qualifications from April 2016, and only qualified persons can use the name career consultant.', 'Through interviews with counselors, we will clarify aptitude and interests, and promote skill improvement and motivation improvement.\nWe will discuss the choice of profession, future career prospects, etc. and clarify the wishes of the person.\nI will explain in detail the content of the work that the counselor wants.\nWe will show you how to improve your skills and encourage you to attend any suitable seminars or training.\nWe will take an inventory of the consultant\'s life, find out hidden talents and aptitudes, and advise them to utilize them for future employment and career changes.\nNot only do we look for a job that suits our wishes, but we also propose jobs that are challenging for the consultant.\nIf you think you need treatment, such as a mental illness, we encourage you to refer a specialist or get into a state of mind to see a psychiatrist.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nUnderstanding and understanding psychology\nCounseling\nDiscovering and solving career challenges', 'Career theory\nCounseling theory\nMental health theory\nVocational ability development\nPersonnel and labor management\nVocational Ability Development Promotion Law\nRelated law