(66, 'Bank of Bank (general occupation)', 6, 6, 21, 'A bank employee (general job) is a job that mainly supports various transactions related to money such as explanation of deposit accounts, application for loans, reception work, etc. at the bank window.\n\nWe perform deposit business that manages customer\'s deposits and savings at the bank counter, and exchange business such as transfer and remittance to settle receivables and debts through the Bank account.\n\nThey are mainly assigned to branch offices and are required to ensure that they carry out specific tasks. If you are in a general position, you will not be transferred or transferred, but you will not be promoted to a managerial position.', 'We will open a customer\'s deposit account and manage deposits and savings at the bank counter.\nThrough a bank account, we perform exchange operations such as transfer and remittance to settle receivables and debts.\nIn order to gain the satisfaction and trust of our customers, we try to serve them politely at the counter.\nBusiness is not limited to Bank business hours, but checks and bills are processed even after business hours.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nOperation of financial system dedicated terminal', '≪Bank business≫\nDeposit\nMoney order\n≪Others≫\nFinance and tax\nSecurities\nInheritance\nReal estate\nEconomy', 'Bank', 'Savings management\nSettlement business\nTransfer and remittance business', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Word processor operator (female)', '21.90', '268.80', 'Starting salary: 219,000 yen (Company size total, 20 to 24 years old)\nAverage: 224,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'None', 'Not clear', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 16:04:29', NULL),
(67, 'Bank of Bank (general occupation)', 6, 6, 21, 'A bank employee (general profession) is a job that not only conducts examinations within the bank such as acquiring loan transactions and selling financial products and office work work, but also sells to individuals and corporations.\n\nWe carry out sales activities such as selling financial products to individuals and corporations, search for clients who need funds, and provide consulting such as loan contracts and utilization of assets.\n\nAs an executive candidate of the headquarters, the general manager will acquire knowledge and skills in a wide range of fields while repeatedly transferring nationwide and changing departments, and will be promoted to a managerial position while accumulating careers.', 'We carry out deposit business that manages customers\' deposits and savings.\nWe carry out sales activities not only for business within the bank but also for individuals and corporations.\nWe provide loans to companies and individuals who need funds.\nThrough the Bank account, we perform the exchange business of transferring and remittance to settle receivables and debts.\nWe provide consulting services such as financing and utilization of assets to individuals and corporations.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nOperation of financial system dedicated terminal', '≪Bank business≫\nDeposit\nLoan\nMoney order\n≪Others≫\nFinance and tax\nSecurities\nInheritance\nReal estate\nEconomy', 'Bank', 'Around customers\nInformation gathering\nCustomer information and product input\nProblem discovery\nPlanning and consultation\nSimulation\nSuggestions, presentations\nFollow up\nOffice work processing', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Insurance agent (male)', '25.10', '596.40', 'Starting salary: 251,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 497,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'None', 'Not clear', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 6, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 16:04:38', NULL),
(68, 'General Secretary', 7, 8, 29, 'General Office work is a job that is in charge of specific Office work work in various organizations such as private companies, government offices, and organizations.\n\nYou can enter various data using a personal computer, collect and process necessary data inside and outside the company, and create and organize documents. We sort and ship mail, respond to telephone calls and respond to visitors, and send e-mails and faxes.\n\nBasically, we do not do jobs that require advanced specialized knowledge and skills, but depending on the company or department, we are entrusted with jobs that require English skills for communication with overseas or jobs that require specialized knowledge such as accounting. Sometimes.', 'According to the instructions from the client, we mainly use a personal computer to collect and process data of various materials such as customer lists, application forms, sales, accounting, accounting, etc., and create and organize documents.\nWe receive and sort mail sent to the company, arrange shipping to business partners, and manage slips.\nBasically, it will be a full-time job within the company, so as a receptionist, we will handle telephone calls and visitor support.\nWe will send e-mails and faxes such as sending necessary messages and data according to the instructions from the requester.\nSince the work in charge and rules differ depending on the type of business and business type of the company to which you belong, we will carry out various office work related work other than these.', 'Document creation / editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nBusiness manner', 'Bookkeeping\nEnglish conversation', 'General companies\nGovernment office\nGroup', 'Telephone answering\nDocument creation and management\nSlip arrangement\nMeeting preparation\nResponding to visitors\nSorting mail service\nCopy or fax\nDaily report creation', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Word processor operator (female)', '21.90', '268.80', 'Starting salary: 219,000 yen (C