(80, 'Judicial scrivener', 7, 8, 22, 'As a familiar lawyer, a judicial scrivener is a job to create legal documents such as real estate registration, commercial registration, deposit, and trial office work.\n\nMy main job is to perform registration work such as real estate registration related to real estate and commercial registration related to corporations. She also performs civil case trial office work, debt consolidation such as voluntary consolidation and self-bankruptcy, depositing to a depository, and criminal accusation and accusation to the public prosecutor\'s office.\n\nIn Japan, where the birthrate is declining and the population is aging, it is expected that there will be more adult guardianship to support property infringement and dignity infringement.', 'We perform real estate registration business when there is a change in the owner of the real estate due to the sale or inheritance of land.\nWe perform commercial registration work when establishing a company, changing officers, or increasing capital.\nWe perform office work work for civil cases in summary courts.\nIn order to solve the multiple debt problem, we perform debt consolidation work such as voluntary consolidation and self-bankruptcy.\nWe perform deposit business when depositing properties such as money and securities to the depository.\nWe will file a criminal accusation and accusation to the public prosecutor\'s office by a parental notice from the client who matches the damage.\nIf you are appointed as an adult guardian, we will protect you by concluding necessary contracts and managing your property on behalf of the person who cannot make a normal judgment due to dementia or disability.\nRegister with the judicial scrivener association in each prefecture and acquire the latest information through training and training.', 'Document editing (MS, Google, etc.)\nApplication document preparation / application\nFinding and resolving issues in application documents\nWard property management\n