(82, 'Aquarium keeper', 8, 2, 44, 'Aquarium keeper is a job to breed and train aquatic and marine life in Aquarium.\n\nIn addition to breeding work and hygiene management, we also provide show training, various event planning according to the season and creatures, inspection and management of Aquarium facilities and facilities, and guidance for visitors.\nIn addition, we will make presentations by observing and researching the ecology of specialized organisms.\n\nMany people have dreams from an early age and become keeper, and since there are few vacancies, there is a flood of applications for recruitment as a narrow gate.', 'The main work is breeding work such as food preparation and feeding of aquatic and marine organisms, and Hygiene management such as cleaning of aquariums.\nWe will consider and prepare for training and directing for shows such as dolphins and seals.\nAs physical condition management, we patrol the aquarium, check and record the health condition and water quality of fish and aquatic organisms, detect signs of illness, and perform observation work to check for abnormalities in fish spawning behavior.\nAs safety management for users, we check the viewing passages and exhibitions, provide guidance, and plan and manage events in the hall.\nWe will make presentations by observing and researching the ecology of aquatic organisms that we specialize in.', 'Feeding and feeding\nManagement of aquatic health\nCleaning the aquarium\nHygiene management\nPlanning of events and exhibitions', 'Ichthyology\nMarine biology\nMarine Mammalogy\nEcology\nVeterinary medicine', 'Aquarium', 'Feeding\nFeeding\nCleaning\nObservation\nRecord\nExhibition production\nEvent planning and management', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Natural science researcher (male)、獣Doctor (male)', '25.60', '573.60', '≪Natural science researcher (male) ≫\nStarting salary: 256,000 yen (Company size total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 478,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)\n\n≪Veterinarian (male) ≫\nStarting 