(83, 'Zoo keeper', 8, 2, 44, 'Animal keeper is a job to raise animals, train them, and study their ecology at the zoo.\n\nIn addition to breeding work and hygiene management, we also provide show training, various event planning according to the season and creatures, inspection and management of Aquarium facilities and facilities, maintenance of contact corners and guidance for visitors. ..\nIn addition, we will make presentations by observing and researching the ecology of specialized organisms.\n\nAt zoos that handle large animals and carnivores, it is important to be aware of the relationship of trust with animals and to understand their ecology. Breeding work is also very important for rare animals.', 'The main work is breeding work such as food preparation and feeding of animals, and Hygiene management such as cleaning of exhibition places and houses.\nLarge animals, carnivorous animals, and animals that require training are taken care of as if they were parents, and they understand the ecology and train while building a relationship of trust.\nIt patrols the park, checks and records the health condition of animals from the gloss, movement, smell, excrement condition, leftover food, etc. of the animal, observes the signs of illness, and assists breeding. increase.\nFor users, we also check the viewing passages and exhibitions, provide guidance, plan and manage events in the park, and train for shows.\nWe will make presentations by observing and researching the ecology of specialized animals.', 'Feeding and feeding\nAnimal health management\nCleaning the kennel\nHygiene management\nPlanning of events and exhibitions', 'Animal ecology\nAnimal Science\nVeterinary medicine', 'Zoo', 'Feeding\nFeeding\nCleaning\nObservation\nRecord\nBreeding\nExhibition production\nEvent planning and management', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Natural science researcher (male), veterinarian (male)', '25.60', '573.60', '≪Natural science researcher (male) ≫\nStarting salary: 256,000 yen (Company size to