(84, 'Veterinarian', 8, 2, 37, 'A veterinarian is a job that provides medical care such as diagnosis, prevention, and treatment of diseases and injuries of domestic animals, and protection and capture of wildlife.\n\nThere are also veterinarians who work as national and local civil servants, and perform a wide range of tasks such as testing and prevention of infectious diseases, protection and breeding of rare and endangered species in domestic and wild animals.\nVeterinarians working at research institutes are also involved in the research and development of veterinary drugs.\n\nDue to the recent pet boom, the number of examinations for rare types of animals is increasing in veterinary hospitals, and a wide range of knowledge and skills are required.', 'Unlike human hospitals, the medical departments are not divided, and various animals are diagnosed, prevented, and treated for illnesses and injuries.\nVeterinary clinics provide medical care, prevention, and treatment for pets, and zoos and aquariums provide medical care, prevention, and treatment for animals and aquatic organisms that live there.\nIn addition to medical examinations, we also provide guidance and consultation on how to keep, discipline, and nutrition.\nIn the livestock industry, we provide medical care, prevention and treatment of diseases of domestic animals such as cattle, horses, pigs and chickens.\nVeterinarians of national civil servants belong to the Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries and the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare, and are responsible for inspecting bacteria and poisons for food animals from overseas, inspecting and preventing infectious diseases of livestock, and preventing their spread in the event of an outbreak.\nLocal government veterinarians carry out a wide range of tasks, including livestock inspection and treatment, pet and wildlife protection, and rabies vaccination.\nVeterinarians working at research institutes are also involved in the field of research and development of veterinary drugs.\nHe provides support for breeding and breeding rare and endangered species, regardless of whether they are wild or wild.', 'Medical examination, examination\nDiagnose\nTreatment, surgery\nOperation of medical record creation software\nCounseling\nTeam management', 'Veterinarian Act\nBasic veterinary medicine\nClinical veterinary medicine\nApplied veterinary medicine\nHygiene', 'Clinic\nZoo\nAquarium\nCow farm\nPig farm\nRacehorse breeding facility\nResearch Institute\nCorporate\nMinistry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries\nMinistry of Health, Labour and Welfare\nQuarantine station\nAnimal quarantine station\nHealth centre\nMeat Sanitation Inspection Center\nNPO corporation', 'Interview\nConsultation\nIdentification\nInformed consent\nTreatment, treatment, surgery\nprescription\nCreating a medical record\nPrognosis observation', 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Veterinarian (male)', '28.10', '404.40', 'Starting salary: 281,000 yen (company scale total, 20-24 years old)\nAverage: 337,000 yen (1,000 people or more, age meter)', 'Graduating from a university with a six -year veterinarian course and passing the national exam.', '31,333人', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 0, NOW(), '2019-03-05 16:09:14', NULL),
(85, 'Dentist', 8, 2, 37, 'A dentist is the job of treating and preventing a patient\'s teeth and oral cavity.\n\nMy main job is to treat the patient\'s teeth and oral cavity, but I am also in charge of all diseases related to the mouth and tongue, and sometimes jaw diseases.\nAs the child grows up, we perform orthodontics, make the teeth look beautiful, such as dentition and whitening, and perform aesthetic dentistry and implant treatment called the third tooth.\n\nIt is easy to think that the treatment range of dentists is only teeth and gums, but in reality, the area above the throat is the area of dentists, and at university hospitals and major general hospitals, surgery for tongue diseases such as tongue cancer and lip and palate Occasionally, general anesthesia is used for several hours of surgery, such as surgery for fissures.', 'We perform treatment of dental caries, production and attachment of dentures, fillings, crowns, inserts, etc., correction of dentition, and treatment of tooth extraction and implants.\nI am also in charge of all diseases related to the mouth and tongue such as good and malignant tumors in the oral region, and sometimes chin diseases.\nWe perform aesthetic dentistry to make teeth look beautiful, such as prevention by cleaning teeth and whitening.\nWe go to schools, children\'s facilities, long-term care facilities, elderly homes, etc. to perform regular dental examinations.', 'Interviews, medical examinations, tests\nDiagnose\nTreatment, tooth cutting\nOperation of medical record creation software\nCounseling\nTeam management', 'Dental Practitioners Act\nBasic dentistry\nClinical dentistry\nOral hygiene', 'Hospital\nUniversity hospital\nClinic\nResearch Institute\nCosmetic companies and pharmaceutical companies', 'Interview\nConsultation\nIdentification\nInformed consent\nTreatment, treatment\nprescription\nCreating a medical record\nPrognosis observation', 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Dentist (male)', '14.30', '576.00', 'Starting salary: 143,000 yen