(86, 'Surgeon', 8, 2, 37, 'A surgeon is a job that mainly treats by surgical techniques such as surgery.\n\nIn order to understand the patient\'s condition, we will conduct an examination and consider an appropriate surgical method. Before the surgery, grasp the nutritional management and physical condition so that the surgery can be performed in a safe condition as well as the surgery, and after the surgery, the recovery status and healing status of the body, and whether there are any signs of complications, etc. Observe the progress.\n\nSurgeons are required to undergo emergency surgery due to sudden changes in the condition of patients brought in by emergency or inpatients, and may be called at night or manage the ward on weekends and holidays.', 'In order to understand the patient\'s condition, we will conduct an examination and consider an appropriate surgical method.\nNot only the method of surgery, but also the range of influence and its order, the safety of the surgical procedure and its countermeasures are considered and presented to patients and their families.\nWe will understand the nutritional management and physical condition before surgery so that the surgery can be performed in a safe condition for the body and mind.\nCreate a prescription that describes the type and amount of medication needed to treat an injury or illness, and how to take it.\nAfter the operation, observe the progress of the body such as recovery status, healing status, and signs of complications.\nI also have academic work, such as visiting other doctors\' surgery, attending conferences, and writing dissertations.', 'Interviews, medical examinations, tests\nDiagnose\nTreatment, tooth cutting\nOperation of medical record creation software\nCounseling\nTeam Management', 'Medical Practitioners Act\nBasic medicine\nClinical medicine\nSocial medicine\nSurgical expertise', 'Hospital\nUniversity hospital\nClinic\nResearch Institute\nCorporate', 'Interview\nConsultation\nIdentification\nI