(97, 'Esthetician', 8, 2, 34, 'An esthetician is a job to care for the whole body except hair for each part such as facial, body, and skin.\n\nWe will check the customer\'s request and lifestyle, inspect the skin condition, and grasp the usual care method in detail.\nIn addition to the treatment at the salon, we propose improvement of usual care methods and lifestyles, and perform facial esthetics, body care, hair removal, etc.\n\nIn addition, we sell skin care products that suit our customers, and we also inform you about campaigns and events other than when you come to the store.\n\nIn order to make customers feel relaxed, it is important to give consideration to conversation during the treatment and creating a space for the salon. It is said that there are 70,000 estheticians, and in addition to esthetic salons, there are a wide range of activities such as bridal salons, beauty salons, and hotels.', 'The treatment includes facial esthetics centered on facial massage, body care such as dieting and slimming, and skin care such as hair removal to treat unwanted hair.\nIn addition to esthetic salons, there are a wide range of workplaces such as bridal salons, beauty salons, and hotels.\nWe prepare linen and equipment to be used in the treatment before opening, manage product inventory, and clean and clean up after closing.\nWe listen to customers\' requests, inspect the condition of the skin, and grasp the usual care methods in detail.\nAs a cosmetologist, we will propose improvements to your usual care methods and lifestyle as well as treatments at the facility.\nWe propose and sell body care and skin care products that suit our customers.\nIn addition to when you come to the store, we will guide you through product and service campaigns and events, and follow up with you.\nPopular beauticians give lectures as beauty advisors and diet counselors, and as influencers of beauty products, they conduct PR activities, product planning, and book writing activities.', 'Faci