(98, 'Manicurist', 8, 2, 34, 'A nail technician is a job to shape and polish the surface of nails and decorate them beautifully at nail salons and beauty salons.\n\nWe will grasp the customer\'s request and the condition of the nails and propose what kind of care, color and art to apply.\nOnce the direction is decided, we will perform nail care and repair, and apply coloring, gels, stickers, and rhinestone nail art.\n\nIn addition, we will introduce and sell nail care products that suit our customers, and will also inform you about campaigns and events other than when you come to the store.\n\nRecently, there is a high demand for more three-dimensional glitter, 3D art, paint art, etc., and we must constantly acquire new technologies.', 'We prepare linen and equipment to be used in the treatment before opening, manage product inventory, and clean and clean up after closing.\nWe confirm the customer\'s fashion and requests, and decide the design while counseling and making suggestions.\nNail care includes filing to shape the nails, buffing to polish the nails, cuticle care to care for the cuticles, and repairs to repair or repair damaged or chipped nails.\nWith nail color, we apply nail polish or gel nails to suit your taste and color them beautifully.\nNail art is decorated with lame enamel, gels and stones, stickers, and designed with artificial nails.\nWe propose and sell nail care, manicure, and accessories that suit our customers.\nIn addition to when you come to the store, we will guide you through product and service campaigns and events, and follow up with you.\nIn order to improve the technique of nails and improve their sense, we will grasp the latest trends, obtain materials, and practice.', 'Nail care\nRepair\nColouring\nNail art\nRelaxation\nCommunication\nCounseling', 'Dermatology\nPhysiological anatomy\nHygiene management\nColor theory\nProduct knowledge', 'Nail beauty salon\nBeauty Salon\nHotel\nBridal salon\nCosmetic company', 'Preparation for opening